{
  "id": "adv_love_2311_08_01",
  "title": "Episode 8 Part 1",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-unknown.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-koh001.wav",
      "text": "（俺と渚は東橋大学に合格し、共に充実した\n四年間を過ごした）"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-unknown.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-koh002.wav",
      "text": "（そして月日は流れ、大学を卒業してから\n数年が過ぎた頃――）"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――文学賞受賞式"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-ngs001.wav",
      "text": "私の小説が文学賞に選ばれるなんて……\nまだ信じられないよ。夢じゃない、よね？"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-unknown.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-koh003.wav",
      "text": "ああ。なんだか感慨深いな……\n受賞作の『波打ち際の君と僕』は\n俺が初めて担当した作品でもあるから"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-ngs002.wav",
      "text": "二人で、あーでもない、こーでもないって\n何回も書き直したよね"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-ngs003.wav",
      "text": "ふふっ、あの時の取材旅行楽しかったな～\n私、まだ鮮明に覚えてるよ\n{user}くんのプロポーズ！"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-unknown.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-koh004.wav",
      "text": "恥ずかしいからやめてくれよ……！"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――『波打ち際の君と僕』"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-ngs004.wav",
      "text": "はぁ～温泉気持ち良かったね～\n女将さんも優しいし、ご飯も美味しいし\nいい旅館だな～"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-unknown.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-koh005.wav",
      "text": "そうだな……\n小説に使えそうなネタは見つかったか？"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-ngs005.wav",
      "text": "せっかくの旅行なのに\nなんだか{user}くん\n今日ずーっとテンション低くない？"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-unknown.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-koh006.wav",
      "text": "そ、そんなことないって！\nあくまで取材旅行なんだから\n渚だってもう少し真面目に……"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-ngs006.wav",
      "text": "相変わらず{user}くんは\nおかたいな～\n少しくらいゆっくりしようよ"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-ngs007.wav",
      "text": "作家にとってはね、行き詰まってる時に\nのんびりして、頭をすっきりさせるのも\n大事な仕事のうちなの！"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-unknown.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-koh007.wav",
      "text": "行き詰まってるのって\nラストシーン……だったよな？"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-ngs008.wav",
      "text": "そうだよ。構成的に\n二人が夫婦になった後の話も\n書きたいんだけど"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-ngs009.wav",
      "text": "今まで、付き合うまでの過程を軸にした\n恋愛小説しか書いたことがなかったから\n夫婦の恋愛って分かんなくて……"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-ngs010.wav",
      "text": "でも、これは私にとって大きな挑戦なの\nここを書ききれば……きっとこの小説は\n間違いなく過去一番の出来になると思う！"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-unknown.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-koh008.wav",
      "text": "ごほんっ。な、なあ、渚……\n俺達、夫婦にならないか……？"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-ngs011.wav",
      "text": "夫婦のフリ、か……\nなんだか、高校生の頃を思い出すね\n恋人のフリをしてもらってた時のこと"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-ngs012.wav",
      "text": "確かに、いいアイデアが浮かぶかもだけど\n私もあの頃と比べて作家として成長したし\nもう少し自分の力で――"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-unknown.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-koh009.wav",
      "text": "違う！"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-ngs013.wav",
      "text": "え……？"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-unknown.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-koh010.wav",
      "text": "渚さん。俺と……結婚して下さい"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-ngs014.wav",
      "text": "フリ……じゃなくて……\nほんとのほんとのプロポーズ？"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-unknown.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-koh011.wav",
      "text": "ああ、俺と結婚して夫婦になって下さい"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-ngs015.wav",
      "text": "ありがとう……嬉しい。ほんとに嬉しいよ\nこちらこそ……よろしくお願いします"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-ngs016.wav",
      "text": "私が夫婦のフリだって勘違いしちゃった時の\n{user}くんの顔ってば\nふふふっ……"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-unknown.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-koh012.wav",
      "text": "そんなに笑うなよ。あの日は朝からずっと\nいつ渚にプロポーズしようか\n一日中考えてたんだから"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-ngs017.wav",
      "text": "そうだったの！？\nだから、なんかテンションが\n低かったんだ～？"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-unknown.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-koh013.wav",
      "text": "はいはい。もうこの話はおしまい\n明日からまた打ち合わせと執筆が\n続くから今日はゆっくり楽しんでくれ"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-ngs018.wav",
      "text": "うん、ありがとう"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-ngs019.wav",
      "text": "よーし、プロットの改稿完了……っと\n{user}くんに指摘された\n部分を直したら、一気に良くなったよ"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-unknown.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-koh014.wav",
      "text": "それは見るのが楽しみだな\n俺が確認している間に\n渚は次の企画を詰めておいてくれ"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-ngs020.wav",
      "text": "ねぇ……{user}くん\nそのことなんだけど……"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-ngs021.wav",
      "text": "私ね……今まで書いたことのない\nジャンルにも挑戦したいなって思ってるの"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-ngs022.wav",
      "text": "恋愛小説を書くのは楽しいし\n評価もしてもらってる"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-ngs023.wav",
      "text": "でも、これからも作家としてやっていくなら\nいろいろと書ける方が仕事の幅が\n広がるかなって"
    },
    {
      "type": "choice_selection",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "挑戦するように勧める",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-unknown.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-koh015.wav",
              "text": "いいと思う。挑戦してみよう"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-ngs024.wav",
              "text": "ほんと！？"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-unknown.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-koh016.wav",
              "text": "あぁ。沢山の新作を走らせて\n作家として充実している今だからこそ\n挑戦する価値があると思う"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-unknown.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-koh017.wav",
              "text": "もちろん、今以上に忙しくなるけど……\n俺がしっかりスケジュールを管理して\n支えるから"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-ngs025.wav",
              "text": "うん、うん……！\nありがとう、{user}くん\n一緒に頑張ろうね！"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-unknown.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-koh018.wav",
              "text": "（その後、渚はミステリーや児童文学など\n様々なジャンルに挑戦し、ヒット作を連発\nドラマ化や映画化までされた）"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": null,
              "speakerName": "",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": null,
              "text": "――夫婦で過ごす、とある日のこと"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-unknown.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-koh019.wav",
              "text": "それじゃあ行ってきます"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-ngs026.wav",
              "text": "あ、待って。ネクタイずれてるよ\n……これで良し、と\nふふ、私がいないと本当にダメなんだから"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-unknown.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-koh020.wav",
              "text": "ああ、そうだな"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-ngs027.wav",
              "text": "……えへへ、そっかそっか～\n隙あり！"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-ngs028.wav",
              "text": "あれ～？"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-unknown.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-koh021.wav",
              "text": "そ、そういう渚だって……顔、真っ赤だぞ"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-ngs029.wav",
              "text": "……だって、{user}くんの\n顔を近くで見ると、いまだに\nドキドキしちゃうんだもん"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-unknown.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-koh022.wav",
              "text": "（頬を赤らめてはにかむ表情は\n小さい頃から変わらないな……）"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-ngs030.wav",
              "text": "{user}くん\nこれからも……ずっと一緒だからね"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-unknown.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-koh023.wav",
              "text": "ああ、もちろんだ"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-unknown.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-koh024.wav",
              "text": "（幼い頃からずっとそばにいてくれた\nこの人を……これからも\nずっとずっと大切にしていこう）"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "やめるように助言する",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-unknown.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-koh025.wav",
              "text": "今はやめておいた方がいいかもな。今でも\nぎりぎりのスケジュールなんだし、もう少し\n落ち着いてから挑戦した方がいいと思う"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-ngs031.wav",
              "text": "……そっか。うん、そうだよね\nよし！"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-unknown.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-koh026.wav",
              "text": "（しばらくすると、渚の人気は\nほどよく落ち着き、仕事もプライベートも\n充実した日々を過ごしている）"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-ngs032.wav",
              "text": "よしっ！"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-unknown.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-koh027.wav",
              "text": "お疲れ様\n最後の校正は俺が今からやっておくよ\n渚はゆっくり休んでくれ"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-ngs033.wav",
              "text": "ダメだよ、{user}くん\nまずは原稿を書き上げた作家を労うのが\n先だよ。いつものしてほしいな～"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-unknown.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-koh028.wav",
              "text": "はいはい、分かったよ\nほら、ぎゅーーー"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-ngs034.wav",
              "text": "ふふっ、私ね、原稿が書き終わって\nこうやって{user}くんに\nぎゅーってされてるこの時間が一番幸せなの"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-ngs035.wav",
              "text": "これからもずーっとずーっと\n私と一緒に居てね\n大好きだよ、{user}くん"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "他社からのオファーを話す",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-unknown.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-koh029.wav",
              "text": "そういえば、新しく出来た出版社から\nオファーがあったな。そこの編集者の方が\n渚の大ファンらしいんだ"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-unknown.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-koh030.wav",
              "text": "「恋愛ものとは違う作品で\n伊吹先生の新たな魅力を見つけたい」と\nおっしゃってたんだよ"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-ngs036.wav",
              "text": "ほんと！？"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-unknown.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-koh031.wav",
              "text": "それじゃあさっそく連絡をとってみるよ"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-unknown.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-koh032.wav",
              "text": "（この時の決断を、俺達は大きく\n後悔することになる――）"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-unknown.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-koh033.wav",
              "text": "（原稿を提出しても、刊行日が決まらず\n印税も振り込まれない。問い詰めようとした\n矢先に、その出版社は倒産）"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-unknown.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-koh034.wav",
              "text": "（新作に費やした情熱と時間が無駄になり\nついに渚は倒れてしまう。結局、他の作品の\n執筆も、ままならなくなってしまった……）"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-unknown.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-koh035.wav",
              "text": "ごめんな、渚\n俺が不甲斐ないばかりに……"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-ngs037.wav",
              "text": "{user}くんのせいじゃないよ\nあの出版社からの仕事を受けるって\n決めたのは私だもん"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-ngs038.wav",
              "text": "それにね、この経験もきっと必要なもの\nだったんだよ。小説家にとって、人生の中で\nいらない経験なんて……一つもない"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_01-ngs039.wav",
              "text": "どんなに辛いことがあっても……\nいつかは全部、小説の糧になるって\n私は信じたいんだ"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
